OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather damp
OL,6,Fin the south this evening but turning
OL,7,Fgenerally dry overnight with the odd
OL,8,Fremaining shower. A chillier night
OL,9,Fwith the possibility of the odd frost
OL,10,Fand fog patch under any lengthy clear
OL,11,Fskies.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRemaining largely cloudy
OL,14,Fthrough the day with a few showers
OL,15,Fpersisting. Occasional brighter breaks
OL,16,Fdeveloping in the south. Somewhat less
OL,17,Fmild but winds generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
